### ========================================
### ARENA GAMER PLATFORM - API Collection
### ========================================

### === USER SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Listar usuarios
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### Buscar usuario por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### Crear usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nuevoJugador",
  "email": "jugador@arenagamer.cl",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "PLAYER"
}

### Actualizar usuario
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic bW9oYW1tZWRBbGlAYXJlbmFnYW1lci5jbDpzdGFmZjEyMw==

{
  "username": "jugadorActualizado",
  "email": "jugador@arenagamer.cl",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "PLAYER"
}

### Eliminar usuario
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Basic bW9oYW1tZWRBbGlAYXJlbmFnYW1lci5jbDpzdGFmZjEyMw==

### Usuarios por rol
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/role/PLAYER

### Usuarios activos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/active

### === STATION SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Listar estaciones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stations

### Buscar estación por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stations/1

### Crear estación
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW5fbGVvOnN0YWZmMTIz

{
  "name": "PC-06",
  "type": "PC",
  "status": "OPERATIONAL",
  "specs": "RTX 4080 / i7 / 16GB RAM",
  "available": true
}

### Estaciones por tipo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stations/type/PC

### Estaciones disponibles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stations/available

### === SESSION SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Listar sesiones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions

### Buscar sesión por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/1

### Iniciar sesión
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "stationId": 1,
  "durationMinutes": 60
}

### Finalizar sesión
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/1/finish

### Cancelar sesión
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/1/cancel

### Sesiones activas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/active

### === ARENA INVENTORY (via Gateway) ===

### Listar productos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/productos

### Buscar producto por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/productos/1

### Crear producto
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/productos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Xbox Series X",
  "categoria": "CONSOLA",
  "stock": 3,
  "precioAlquiler": 3000.0
}

### Actualizar stock
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/productos/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cantidad": -1
}

### === ARENA RESERVAS (via Gateway) ===

### Listar reservas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservas

### Crear reserva
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": 1,
  "estacionId": 1,
  "fecha": "2026-08-01",
  "bloqueHorario": "14:00-15:00"
}

### Cambiar estado de reserva
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reservas/1/estado
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estado": "CONFIRMADA",
  "comentario": "Confirmada por staff"
}

### === ARENA WALLET (via Gateway) ===

### Listar billeteras
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billeteras

### Buscar billetera por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billeteras/1

### Crear billetera
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billeteras
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idUsuario": 1,
  "saldo": 10000.0,
  "puntosFidelizacion": 0
}

### Recargar saldo
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billeteras/1/recargas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "monto": 5000.0
}

### === LOYALTY SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Ver perfil de lealtad
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loyalty/1

### Acreditar puntos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loyalty/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "amount": 100,
  "reason": "Sesión completada"
}

### Canjear puntos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loyalty/redeem
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "rewardId": 1
}

### === HARDWARE MONITOR (via Gateway) ===

### Ver estado de equipos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hardware/status

### Reportar temperatura
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hardware/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pcId": "PC-01",
  "cpuTemp": 75.0,
  "gpuTemp": 80.0
}

### === NOTIFICATION SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Ver logs de notificaciones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/logs

### Enviar notificación
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "jugador@arenagamer.cl",
  "message": "Tu sesión ha finalizado",
  "channel": "EMAIL"
}

### === TOURNAMENT SERVICE (via Gateway) ===

### Listar torneos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tournaments

### Crear torneo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tournaments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Torneo Valorant",
  "game": "Valorant",
  "maxTeams": 8,
  "userId": 1
}